summary: Rep Comemeur s                 receives the title "Commemorator of the Year" in France. The award is given to a person who has made a significant contribution to the country's political and social progress. For more information on the award, go to: http://www.cnn.com/2013/01/14/nomination/commemoration/top-10-words-of-year.
